```cedar
let creator = context.created.contains(context.access_key);
```

## Step 2: Define the condition to check if someone other than the principal reviewed the resource
```cedar
let has_other_reviewer = context.has_other_reviewers;
```

## Step 3: Combine the conditions to check if both are true
```cedar
creator && has_other_reviewer;
